{"id":15564,"date":"2024-02-15T18:19:14","date_gmt":"2020-10-15T12:49:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=15564"},"modified":"2022-12-02T16:05:37","modified_gmt":"2022-12-02T10:35:37","slug":"partition-design","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/partition-design\/","title":{"rendered":"Pretty Partition Design Ideas To Make Your Home Look Functional And Fabulous"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Create more space with a statement, go for these gorgeous partition designs for your home<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Most modern homes have an underwhelmingly inefficient open-layout these days. It not only kills privacy but also does not create a dedicated space to separate the important areas of your home. Keeping all these constraints along with that of space in mind, we have selected partition design ideas that you can include in your home interior plan with ease.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Designed to separate the living area from the dining space and making sure that one area does not remain all dark, these latest partition design ideas will make your home more functional, fun and liveable for your family!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking for a wooden separator, fixed partition, designer partition, or more ideas for your home? Refer to our recommendations and transform your home in a jiffy!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Glass Partition Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Preferred for all the right reasons, a glass partition design ensures that your home gets adequate light all through the day. Also, a glass partition design has an inherent elegance that you can enhance by using a pop of coloured glass in between the same.&nbsp; Give this partition design some character by interplaying glass within a wooden or metal frame.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175622\/glass-partition-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"A glass partition design between the living and dining room inherent elegance is room partition ideas.\" class=\"wp-image-15572\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175622\/glass-partition-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175622\/glass-partition-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175622\/glass-partition-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175622\/glass-partition-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Glass partition design is here to stay choose it well then<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Wooden Partition Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Simple, streamlined, and low on maintenance a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/wooden-partition-designs-between-living-room-and-dining-room\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">wooden partition design<\/a> quickly fits into your home. And why not? For all the right reasons and iterations, you can tweak this partition design and design one in your choice of wood. Let it speak for itself by creating seamlessness in your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175650\/wooden-separator-design.jpg\" alt=\"The wooden separator between living and dining room is chic and minimal even the kitchen has a wooden partition.\" class=\"wp-image-15578\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175650\/wooden-separator-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175650\/wooden-separator-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175650\/wooden-separator-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175650\/wooden-separator-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Chic and minimal, a wooden partition design leaves an everlasting impression<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get 20% extra space with partition designs in your home\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15143121\/get-20-extra-space-with-partition-designs-in-your-home.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Metal Partition Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Nothing whispers more sophistication in your home than a personalised metal partition design. Take inspiration from India\u2019s heritage art or go for simpler patterns but interplay it with a metal partition design and it will win your attention. This design demarcates areas but does not completely block the view &#8211; just what you need for your modern apartment, right?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175628\/metal-partition-wall-type.jpg\" alt=\"Metal partition design personalised between living and dining room is classy.\" class=\"wp-image-15573\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175628\/metal-partition-wall-type.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175628\/metal-partition-wall-type-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175628\/metal-partition-wall-type-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175628\/metal-partition-wall-type-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Go for a metal partition design to keep it classy and subtly private<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Artistic Partition Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You can conveniently turn a partition design in a piece of art or decor at home with some thought. This artistic partition design just hits the right tangent for the same. Resurrected through partially visible metal strips, it fluidly lets the wood chunks come together to create an artistic partition design. Don\u2019t you love it already?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175612\/artistic-home-partition-design.jpg\" alt=\"Artistic home partition design in a mix of metal and wood look a piece of decor at home.\" class=\"wp-image-15570\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175612\/artistic-home-partition-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175612\/artistic-home-partition-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175612\/artistic-home-partition-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175612\/artistic-home-partition-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Mix of metal, wood, and out of the box thought makes this artistic partition design unforgettable<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">An Ornate Partition Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Wood and metal create a combination that will make your guests go all gaga with their compliments. Choose them for a modern partition design already? Its intricate metal design occupies the central and the wooden framework grants a rich texture to the same. Select this modern partition design without a second thought!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175639\/ornate-partition-design-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Wood and intricate metal create a modern partition design and grants a rich texture is partition ideas.\" class=\"wp-image-15575\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175639\/ornate-partition-design-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175639\/ornate-partition-design-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175639\/ornate-partition-design-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175639\/ornate-partition-design-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>An eclectic play of wooden and intricate metal patterns create a modern partition design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Abstract Partition Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Love to add some madness with the method? Well, well, give this abstract partition design the benefit of doubt. In the first go, it might look like an outlandish design, however, it grows on you with its artistic interpretation for a separator. And along with its function, it does a great service to the aesthetic appeal of your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175607\/abstract-partition-design.jpg\" alt=\"Abstract partition wall types of artistic interpretation for a separator and brings aesthetic appeal to your home.\" class=\"wp-image-15569\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175607\/abstract-partition-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175607\/abstract-partition-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175607\/abstract-partition-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175607\/abstract-partition-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Like bold partition ideas? This abstract partition design is created just for you then!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Partition Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Metal and cement if managed well can create wonders. This modern partition design makes a brilliant design.&nbsp; With metal partitions gently framed through a rustic wall, it lives up to an interesting interpretation for a modern partition design. Hasn\u2019t this design got your attention already?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175633\/modern-home-partition-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"House partition design with metal partitions gently framed through a rustic wall makes a brilliant design.\" class=\"wp-image-15574\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175633\/modern-home-partition-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175633\/modern-home-partition-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175633\/modern-home-partition-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175633\/modern-home-partition-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Balance the strengths of metal and rustic texture of cement to create a magical modern partition design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Contemporary Partition Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Etched like a piece of art, this contemporary partition design juxtaposes aesthetics and functionality. It does justice to creating not just a commonplace partition design but rather works as its own ode to art that you cannot help but notice whenever you pass it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175617\/contemporary-house-partition-design.jpg\" alt=\"Contemporary partition design creates an art oasis that seamlessly separates your spaces at home partition ideas.\" class=\"wp-image-15571\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175617\/contemporary-house-partition-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175617\/contemporary-house-partition-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175617\/contemporary-house-partition-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/15175617\/contemporary-house-partition-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Contemporary partition design is just right to create an art oasis that seamlessly separates your spaces at home<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Loved all these partition ideas for your home and in a dilemma about which one to go ahead with? Allow us to assist you with a consultation for the same, we would be glad to design the perfect partition design for your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/room-divider-ideas\/\">Room Divider Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/living-room-partition-design-ideas\/\">Living Room Partition&nbsp; Design Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a 